#

Honey Ricotta Toast

5 min
$3.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

DairyGluten (if using regular bread)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Protein

Cuisine:

ItalianAmerican

Course:

BreakfastSnack

Tags:

QuickHealthyBreakfastSnack

Description

A delightful blend of creamy ricotta cheese and sweet honey on crispy toast, perfect for breakfast or a snack!

Ingredients

  • bread (your choice): 2 slices
  • ricotta cheese: 1/2 cup
  • honey: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh fruit (like berries or sliced banana): optional, for topping
  • cinnamon (optional): a pinch
